{"type": "article", "id": 17840, "title": "纸盒谷物包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-20T07:10:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143101wPn0TcF7Jmev9rsI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t购买大米小麦之类的谷物通常是不需要包装的，一个透明的袋子足可说明一切。俄罗斯的 Yarmarka 坚持使用纸盒包装，他们请来设计事务所 :OTVETDESIGN 做包装设计。在彩色的盒子正中间画了一个口袋，中间印着对应的粮食，一头连接着叉子，表达可食用的概念。四周环绕着更大的颗粒和使用说明，用了有手绘感的图案，很直观。重要的是盒子带给人清新活泼的感受，近似于饼干等零食，让人觉得亲近生动。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143058MjrpJEFBsyvQdlCV.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143059NLWvg5A7zoCikufj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143059JMtdpiUQ2mfkv719.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143100xVUnPc1MdYZSwBtr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143100fLjRHDcOIMTrKbdS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}